SUMMARY:The Hammer and The Hatchet
DESCRIPTION:The Hammer and The Hatchet present: \nAn Evening of Tall Tales and Truths at The Brown County Playhouse. Friday\, May 15.  \nJoe’s Truck Stop\, Abe Partridge\, and The Hammer and The Hatchet will share their songs and stories and the inspiration behind them. Sometimes odd\, sometimes unexpected\, sometimes wonderful. Always original. We’re excited to announce this showcase of bands\, storytellers and friends as we gather in community.  Experience their music\, art\, and good humor on the historic stage at the Brown County Playhouse. \n\nBUY TICKETS\n \n \n \n \nBUY TICKETS
URL:https://browncountyplayhouse.org/event/the-hammer-and-the-hatchet-2026/
LOCATION:Brown County Playhouse\, 70 S. Van Buren St\, Nashville\, IN\, 47448\, United States
CATEGORIES:Americana,Country,Featured Event,Folk
ATTACH;FMTTYPE=image/jpeg:https://browncountyplayhouse.org/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/2026-HH_web_event.jpg
END:VEVENT
