SUMMARY:An Evening of Classic Country feat. The Roundups and Bakersfield Bound
DESCRIPTION:An Evening of Classic Country featuring Bakersfield Bound & The Roundups Brown County Playhouse \nA classic country double-header you won’t want to miss. Bakersfield Bound and The Roundups join forces for one night of the songs and sounds that never go out of style — rich harmonies\, amazing fiddle playing\, fantastic guitar picking\, and stories that still ring true. Whether you grew up on this music or you’re just finding it\, this is an evening worth dressing up for. \nBUY TICKETS\n\n 
